WEBVTT

00:00.490 --> 00:04.220
Lain, is suicide the only thing left for me to do?

00:05.930 --> 00:07.570
Is there no other option?

00:09.500 --> 00:12.140
Do I have to die?

00:13.980 --> 00:15.030
No!

00:16.080 --> 00:17.760
I don’t want that!

00:20.260 --> 00:22.150
I don’t want anyone to control me.

00:23.330 --> 00:24.610
Who does?

00:26.010 --> 00:27.630
Aren’t you the same way, Lain?

00:29.660 --> 00:31.930
You were scared and scared and didn’t know what to do.

00:33.360 --> 00:36.210
Please Lain, help me.

00:38.210 --> 00:38.750
Please.
